M|Reve|it|[ ] Gross vs. net rv clearly labeled
M|Reve|it|[ ] rv growth rate > cost growth rate
M|Reve|it|[ ] ARPU/ARPA tracked by cohort (not just blended)
M|Reve|- [ |Top cs <10%, Top 10 <40%
M|Rete|it|[ ] Monthly churn <5% (ideally <2%)
M|Rete|it|[ ] rv churn vs. logo churn compared
M|Rete|it|[ ] NRR >100% (ideally >120%)
M|Rete|it|[ ] Quick Ratio >2 (ideally >4)
M|Coho|it|[ ] Recent cohorts perform same or better than older cohorts
M|Coho|it|[ ] rv retention tracked, not just logo retention
M|Coho|it|[ ] Expansion analyzed by cohort
M|Coho|tx|---
M|Red |Chec|
M|Red |it|[ ] rv churn > logo churn (losing big cs)
M|Red |it|[ ] ARPU growing but cs count shrinking (mix shift, not improvement)
M|Red |it|[ ] Newer cohorts churn faster than older cohorts (PMF degradation)
M|Red |it|[ ] NRR <100% (contracting, not expanding)
M|Red |it|[ ] Quick Ratio <2 (leaky bucket)
M|Red |it|[ ] Discounts >20% or refunds >10% (pricing/pd problems)
M|Red |it|[ ] rv concentration >50% in top 10 cs (risk)
M|Red |it|[ ] Expansion rv <10% of total MRR (monetization problem)
M|Red |tx|---
